snippet.title: Revenant | Expansion Trailer
snippet.description:
The Revenant expansion for EVE Online is live! Join forces with the Deathless and strike at the heart of darkness as you explore thrilling new opportunities, fearsome ships, powerful weapons, mercenary dens that harness new resources, and new ways to activate and unify your corporation.  

Learn more about the Revenant expansion at: https://www.eveonline.com/news/view/revenant-is-here
and https://www.eveonline.com/now/revenant 

Discord - https://discord.gg/eveonline
